These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, rock, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, spanish, egyptian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
2. the spanish is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the spanish is in an even position##4
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | salsa     | rock    |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | spanish          | nigerian   |
| Sport         | baseball | skiing | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, broccoli, potato
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, dancing
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, scientist, pilot
1. the pilot is the person eating potato##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the pilot##3
3. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the scientist is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the pilot is in an even position##4
6. the pilot is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | cauliflower     | potato  | broccoli  |
| Hobby   | dancing | hiking | baking    |
| Job     | nurse      | pilot    | scientist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: banana, pomegranate, blueberry
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, soul, jazz
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person eating banana##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of trance##1
4. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating banana##1
5. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | banana         | blueberry     | pomegranate   |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | trance     | jazz |
| Sport         | snowboarding | badminton | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, fanta
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, electrician
3 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, bird
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the electrician##1
3. the architect is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
6. the mechanic is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | fanta  | tea |
| Job        | electrician | mechanic  | architect |
| Pet        | hamster | guinea-pig | bird         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, scientific, adventure
There are 3 different nationalities: german, nigerian, british
3 different pets are kept: pony, rat, ferret
1. the german is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
2. the nigerian is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | action  | scientific  |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | german | british |
| Pet           | rat  | ferret    | pony    |

