.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, writing
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, helicopter, airplane
1. the person drinking water is between the person driving the airplane and the person who's hobby is writing##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate  | water  | iced-tea        |
| Hobby       | writing | puzzles | magic-tricks |
| Transport   | ship    | helicopter   | airplane   |

