.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, martial-arts, crime
3 different pets are kept: horse, dog, fish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rugby, ice-hockey
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the owner of the horse and the person watching crime movies##2
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | martial-arts        | crime |
| Pet           | horse   | dog      | fish     |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby | climbing    |

