.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, plum, carrot
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, librarian, chef
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, basketball, cycling
1. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the chef and the person eating carrot##2
3. the librarian is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Food    | artichoke   | plum | carrot       |
| Job     | chef  | writer  | librarian |
| Sport   | basketball | water-polo  | cycling       |

