.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, chess, magic-tricks
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, egyptian, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, frog
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
4. the indonesian is on the right of the egyptian##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | chess | fishing | magic-tricks |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | egyptian  | indonesian     |
| Pet           | turtle     | frog     | ferret          |

