.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, lawyer, designer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, disaster, animation
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, indonesian, indian
1. the lawyer is on the far right##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the turkish is on the left or right of the indian##3
4. the writer is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the indian is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | designer | writer        | lawyer   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | animation | spy    |
| Nationality   | indian         | turkish      | indonesian |

