3. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | fanta | water     |
| Sport       | ice-hockey | biathlon          | parkour |
| Transport   | roller     | train          | car       |

