3. the bartender is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the accountant is the owner of the hamster##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job     | accountant      | designer | bartender |
| Pet     | hamster | snake      | mouse           |
| Sport   | skateboarding | ice-hockey  | soccer    |

