1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
3. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | 7up | fanta      | hot-chocolate     |
| Pet         | hamster  | frog | mouse        |
| Transport   | bus | trike    | subway |

