4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | coffee | juice  | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | d&b    | gospel       |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | dutch | french   |

