.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, spy
3 different pets are kept: turtle, frog, pony
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person watching time-travel movies##2
2. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the frog##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
7. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing      | puzzles | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | satire      | spy    |
| Pet           | pony      | turtle        | frog       |

 